    "name": "自在城镇",
    "steam_appid": 3115220,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Town to City》诚邀您加入这款温馨的城市建设游戏，摆脱网格的限制，打造一个美丽而繁华的社区。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由放置房屋、商店、便利设施和自然元素，以此取悦您的居民，并鼓励更多的家庭搬迁至此。随着人口的增长，您的野心也会随之增长，继而建造多个可以单独发展或共同兴旺的城镇，让整个区域繁荣兴盛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在剧情或沙盒模式下，您可以自由地按照自己的节奏打造城镇，以像素级的精度放置每个花坛。或者，您也可以优先发展经济，将城镇发展成为一个繁荣的城市。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115220/extras/84a739309383159042afbcffba3cf2d8.poster.avif?t=1772140952\" width=616 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115220/extras/84a739309383159042afbcffba3cf2d8.webm?t=1772140952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115220/extras/84a739309383159042afbcffba3cf2d8.mp4?t=1772140952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>建造城市</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真正的无网格建造系统让您可以自由地按照个人喜好布置城镇。您可以有序地规划房屋排列和城市区域布局，也可以通过蜿蜒的街道和小巷连接住宅、便利设施、公园和广场，有机地向外发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115220/extras/ba7a3478ba972ea4a22a63bbc891b674.poster.avif?t=1772140952\" width=616 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115220/extras/ba7a3478ba972ea4a22a63bbc891b674.webm?t=1772140952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115220/extras/ba7a3478ba972ea4a22a63bbc891b674.mp4?t=1772140952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>释放创意</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽情美化您的居住区，海量自定义选项任您选择。设置照明，种植花卉，打造林间公园，装饰房屋和建筑，使其相互映衬或形成鲜明对比。以精美的体素图形为基础，轻松打造出令人赞叹的美景，并使用游戏中的拍照模式将其记录下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115220/extras/bba765dc7473da690a4df8dfc8804700.poster.avif?t=1772140952\" width=616 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115220/extras/bba765dc7473da690a4df8dfc8804700.webm?t=1772140952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115220/extras/bba765dc7473da690a4df8dfc8804700.mp4?t=1772140952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扶持社区</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着您的城镇日益繁荣，您就需要满足不断增长的人口的需求。修建一些无论是工人、工匠或是中产阶级都能用到的设施吧，同时也别忽略个别居民的特定需求。了解来到城镇上的每一位居民，目睹他们在您提供的房屋中安顿下来、组建家庭吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115220/extras/4727f51c9672b463b3256be1974781ce.poster.avif?t=1772140952\" width=616 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115220/extras/4727f51c9672b463b3256be1974781ce.webm?t=1772140952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115220/extras/4727f51c9672b463b3256be1974781ce.mp4?t=1772140952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发展经济</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为工人分配工作，研究新的建筑和装饰，挖掘居住区的潜力，将其发展为繁华的商业中心。随着第一座城镇逐渐无法满足扩张需求，您需要在边界之外修建新的城镇。这些城镇将通过贸易和旅行路线相互连接，以此为您带来农业和旅游业方面的全新发展机遇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重要特色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-          <strong>完整的战役和沙盒模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-          <strong>真正的无网格城市建造工具</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-          <strong>城镇和居民管理</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-          <strong>丰富的自定义项目</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-          <strong>科技树</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-          <strong>拍照模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-          <strong>美丽的体素艺术风格</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-          舒缓放松的配乐</strong></p>",
